*%=== JCL Features ==========================
*JCLBegin:           "<1B>%-12345X@PJL JOB<0A>"
*JCLToPSInterpreter: "@PJL ENTER LANGUAGE=POSTSCRIPT<0A>"
*JCLEnd:             "<04><1B>%-12345X"


*% Media Input Source
*OpenUI *InputSlot/Paper Source: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 20 AnySetup *InputSlot
*DefaultInputSlot: AutoSelect
*InputSlot AutoSelect/Auto-selected by the printer: "<</MediaPosition 1>>setpagedevice"
*InputSlot MultifunTray/Multipurpose Input Tray: "<</MediaPosition 3>>setpagedevice"
*InputSlot AutoFeed/Automatic Feeder Tray: "<</MediaPosition 4>>setpagedevice"
*InputSlot Tray1/Optional Input Tray 1: "<</MediaPosition 5>>setpagedevice"
*InputSlot Tray2/Optional Input Tray 2: "<</MediaPosition 7>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *InputSlot


*OpenUI *MediaType/Paper Type: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 JCLSetup *MediaType
*DefaultMediaType: Plain
*MediaType Plain/Plain:	"@PJL SET PAPERTYPE=PLAIN<0A>"
*MediaType Thick/Thick: "@PJL SET PAPERTYPE=TOUGH<0A>"
*MediaType Envelope/Envelope: "@PJL SET PAPERTYPE=ENVELOPE<0A>"
*MediaType Transparency/Transparency: "@PJL SET PAPERTYPE=TRANSPARENCY<0A>"
*MediaType Cardstock/Cardstock: "@PJL SET PAPERTYPE=CARDSTOCK<0A>"
*MediaType Label/Label: "@PJL SET PAPERTYPE=LABELS<0A>"
*MediaType Kleenex/Thin paper: "@PJL SET PAPERTYPE=TISSUE<0A>"
*MediaType Thicker/Thicker paper: "@PJL SET PAPERTYPE=TOUGHER<0A>"
*MediaType Recycled/Recycled Paper: "@PJL SET PAPERTYPE=RECYCLED<0A>"
*CloseUI: *MediaType

*OpenUI *Duplex/Two-Sided: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *Duplex
*DefaultDuplex: None
*Duplex None/Off: "<</Duplex false /Tumble false>>setpagedevice"
*Duplex DuplexNoTumble/Long Edge: "<</Duplex true /Tumble false>>setpagedevice"
*Duplex DuplexTumble/Short Edge: "<</Duplex true /Tumble true>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Duplex

*OpenUI *Collate/Collate: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 JCLSetup *OutputBins
*DefaultCollate: False
*Collate False/Off: ""
*Collate True/On: ""
*CloseUI: *Collate


*CloseGroup: General


*OpenGroup: PrintoutMode/Paper


*OpenUI *Resolution/Resolution: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 JCLSetup *Resolution
*DefaultResolution: 600dpi
*Resolution 600dpi/600dpi: "@PJL SET RESOLUTION=600X600<0A>@PJL SET BITSPERPIXEL=1<0A>"
*Resolution 1200dpi/1200dpi: "@PJL SET RESOLUTION=600X600<0A>@PJL SET BITSPERPIXEL=2<0A>"
*CloseUI: *Resolution

*OpenUI *Booklet/Booklet: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 60 AnySetup *Booklet
*DefaultBooklet: False
*Booklet True/on: ""
*Booklet False/Off: ""
*CloseUI: *Booklet

*% FeedEdge
*OpenUI *FeedEdge/Feed Orientation: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 15.0 JCLSetup *FeedEdge
*DefaultFeedEdge: ShortEdge
*FeedEdge ShortEdge/Short Edge Feed: ""
*FeedEdge LongEdge/Long Edge Feed: ""
*CloseUI: *FeedEdge


*OpenUI *Density/Density: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 50.0 JCLSetup *Density
*DefaultDensity: Normal
*Density LessLight/LessLight: "@PJL SET DENSITY=LEVEL0<0A>"
*Density Light/Light: "@PJL SET DENSITY=LEVEL1<0A>"
*Density Normal/Normal: "@PJL SET DENSITY=LEVEL2<0A>"
*Density Dark/Dark: "@PJL SET DENSITY=LEVEL3<0A>"
*Density LessDark/LessDark: "@PJL SET DENSITY=LEVEL4<0A>"
*CloseUI: *Density

*OpenUI *TonerMode/Toner Save: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 JCLSetup *TonerMode
*DefaultTonerMode: False
*TonerMode False/Off: "@PJL SET TONERSAVE=DISABLE<0A>"
*TonerMode True/On: "@PJL SET TONERSAVE=ENABLE<0A>"
*CloseUI: *TonerMode

*OpenUI *FineMode/FineMode: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 JCLSetup *FineMode
*DefaultFineMode: False
*FineMode False/Off: "@PJL SET FINE=OFF<0A>"
*FineMode True/On: "@PJL SET FINE=ON<0A>"
*CloseUI: *FineMode


*CloseGroup: PrintoutMode



*% === PinPrint ===
*OpenGroup: PinPrint/Pin Print

*OpenUI *LockedPinPrint/Enale PIN Print(PIN 4-digits): Boolean
*OrderDependency: 30 AnySetup *LockedPinPrint
*DefaultLockedPinPrint: False
*LockedPinPrint False/OFF:""
*LockedPinPrint True/ON:""
*?LockedPinPrint: "
  save
    currentpagedevice /LockedPinPrint get
    {(True)}{(False)}ifelse = flush
  restore
"
*End
*CloseUI: *LockedPinPrint

